      "text": "Recommended flow\n\n1. Browser calls App Runner\n2. App Runner runs ECS task\n3. Worker downloads from S3\n4. Worker publishes progress to Redis\n5. App Runner streams SSE to Browser\n6. Worker uses NAT for OpenAI API",
